alchemist/it.unibo.alchemist.boundary.fxui.impl/EffectGroupCell

EffectGroupCell

open class EffectGroupCell<P : Position2D<out P>?> : AbstractEffectCell<T>

This ListView cell implements the AbstractEffectCell for containing an EffectGroup. It has a name that identifies the EffectGroup and when clicked should open a javafx.scene.control.ListView to show the effects the group is composed of.

Parameters

<P>

the position type
